 way, the "Go back" link above is not a static link (of course) but a dynamic one. It was created using an "insert tag" called <em>link::back</em>. There are a few insert tags in Contao that help you include dynamic data.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href="http://www.contao.org/en/insert-tags.html" target="_blank" title="Learn more about insert tags">Learn more about insert tags</a><br />', '', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', NULL, '', 0x00000000000000000000000000000000, '', '', 0, 300, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', NULL, '', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:"";i:1;s:0:"";}', 'a:2:{i:0;s:0:"";i:1;s:0:"";}', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', 0, 0, '', 0, '', '', '', '', '' );
